{
  "stem": "19969.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 77,
      "text": "But it happened to be in my zone of attack.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 78,
      "text": "And the information was that if we went into Dachau, that it was a politically sensitive area.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 79,
      "text": "That's the way it came over the radio.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 80,
      "text": "Well, that doesn't mean a damn thing to me, really.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 81,
      "text": "I don't pay a whole lot of attention to it because my mission was to take Munich.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I didn't know what a concentration camps was.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'd never heard of it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Neither had any American soldier.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so I-- well, we assumed from the word, of course, that they were concentration-- that they were prisoners there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we had absolutely and utterly no information in the American Army about concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There might have been some at higher headquarters.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I doubt it because none of it was ever disseminated, at least to the troops.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I didn't pay much attention to that, to tell you the truth.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the next morning, I looked at my map.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I saw where the concentration camp was, right outside of the city of Dachau.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I had my left force, commanded by my executive officer, pass to the left of the camp, attacking towards Munich, and my right force, that I was commanding, attacking to the right of the camp.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I didn't want to get slowed down by any concentration camp because I didn't figure that was a military objective.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I didn't see how I was going to harm me any.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my mission was to take Munich.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I jumped off the next morning in that formation, in my two units.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the concentration camp was in-between my two units-- my right units and my left.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Major Kessler.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was my executive officer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then I had the right unit.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
